# User v1

## Get balance 

```shell
curl "https://<%= config[:api_domain] %>/v1/user/balance"
  -H "<%= config[:authorization_method] %>"
```

```javascript
const <%= config[:sdk_class_name] %> = require('<%= config[:sdk_name] %>');

let api = <%= config[:sdk_class_name] %>.authorize('<api_token>');
let balance = api.balance();
```

